        "description": "N=11 production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm constructs tested across two independent laboratories. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison per ASME V&V 40. Gradation 3 requires multiple production-representative samples with documented traceability."
      },
      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production lots, tested at FDA CDRH and an independent contract laboratory. Sample traceability documented (lot numbers, assembly torque records). Inter-laboratory CV on stiffness = 4.1%, within acceptable range. Achieves Gradation 3."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/factor/test-conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
