      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Eq. 1 for stiffness (mean 1.31, max 1.78), yield force (mean 1.44, max 1.89), and force@40mm (mean 1.19, max 1.61). All 33 construct-QoI pairs satisfy E/uval < 1.96. Percent differences all < 10%. Comparison methodology peer-reviewed and archived in DAR-2023-042, §6. Achieves Gradation 3."
