      },
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three primary endpoints evaluated in ASTM F1717 and referenced in FDA's 2021 guidance on spinal implant submissions. These QoIs directly inform the COU decision (whether FEA can substitute for or augment bench testing). Linkage documented in DAR-2023-042, §2. Achieves Gradation 3."
